The State Tax Increment Financing Commission is hereby created as an independent agency of the state within the meaning of KRS Chapter 12. The commission shall be composed of the following members:
The secretary of the Finance and Administration Cabinet, who shall be the chair thereof;
The state budget director;
The secretary of the Cabinet for Economic Development;
The secretary of the Tourism, Arts and Heritage Cabinet;
The chair of the Kentucky Economic Development Finance Authority;
The dean of the University of Kentucky Gatton College of Business and Economics; and
The dean of the University of Louisville College of Business and Public Administration.
